<td bgcolor=3D"#ffffff" class=3D"Style2">=0D
<p align=3D"justify"><b>Les films de la r&eacute;gion en festival et sur le=
s &eacute;crans...</b></p>=0D
<p align=3D"justify"><b><span style=3D"text-decoration: underline;">Fiction=
